('Crystal Cookies', 'crystal-cookies', 'sativa', 16.8, 0.5, array['tingly', 'happy', 'hungry', 'sleepy']::text[], array['spicy', 'vanilla', 'skunk']::text[], array['humulene', 'myrcene', 'caryophyllene']::text[], 'moderate', 9, '550-650 g/m²', '650-800 g/plant', 'Crystal Cookies — A sativa prized for its energizing, cerebral lift that suits daytime creativity and social sessions. Expect spicy, vanilla, skunk flavors with dominant humulene, most often leaving users feeling tingly and happy.'),
('Crystal Gelato', 'crystal-gelato', 'hybrid', 14.2, 1.0, array['euphoric', 'sleepy', 'relaxed', 'giggly', 'hungry']::text[], array['lemon', 'cheese', 'mango']::text[], array['ocimene', 'linalool', 'limonene']::text[], 'hard', 9, '525-625 g/m²', '650-800 g/plant', 'Crystal Gelato — A balanced hybrid offering the best of both worlds — a smooth head high that settles into gentle body calm. Expect lemon, cheese, mango flavors with dominant ocimene, most often leaving users feeling euphoric and sleepy.'),
('Crystal Runtz', 'crystal-runtz', 'indica', 17.9, 0.7, array['uplifted', 'talkative', 'tingly']::text[], array['floral', 'spicy', 'earthy']::text[], array['terpinolene', 'limonene', 'humulene']::text[], 'easy', 8, '500-600 g/m²', '550-700 g/plant', 'Crystal Runtz — An indica known for deep body relaxation, best reserved for evenings and lazy nights in. Expect floral, spicy, earthy flavors with dominant terpinolene, most often leaving users feeling uplifted and talkative.')
